<item>
  <title>Kaggle CLI Setup</title>
  <dc:creator>盧晉偉 </dc:creator>
  <link>https://ch1nv.github.io/luchinwei/notes/kaggle-cli-setup.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 




<section id="目的" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="目的">目的</h2>
<p>記錄 Kaggle CLI 的安裝、API token 設定與常用指令，作為之後下載資料集與重現實驗環境時的參考。</p>
</section>
<section id="安裝" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="安裝">安裝</h2>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb1" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode bash code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb1-1"><span class="ex" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">pip</span> install kaggle</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="api-token" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="api-token">API Token</h2>
<ol type="1">
<li>到 Kaggle Account 頁面建立 API token。</li>
<li>下載 <code>kaggle.json</code>。</li>
<li>將 token 放到 Kaggle CLI 預設讀取的位置。</li>
</ol>
</section>
<section id="常用指令" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="常用指令">常用指令</h2>
<div class="code-copy-outer-scaffold"><div class="sourceCode" id="cb2" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode bash code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode bash"><span id="cb2-1"><span class="ex" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">kaggle</span> datasets list</span>
<span id="cb2-2"><span class="ex" style="color: null;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">kaggle</span> datasets download <span class="at" style="color: #657422;
background-color: null;
font-style: inherit;">-d</span> owner/dataset-name</span></code></pre></div></div>
</section>
<section id="待補" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="待補">待補</h2>
<ul>
<li>Windows / macOS / Linux 的 token 路徑差異</li>
<li>常見錯誤訊息與解法</li>
<li>專案中實際用到的資料集下載流程</li>
</ul>


</section>

